<div style="background:#FAFAFA; --darkbg:#333; border-radius:0 0 6px 6px; padding:1px 5px; margin:2px 4px;">
<ul><li>The <b><a href="/Halopedia:Community" title="Halopedia:Community">community portal</a></b> is the central place to find out what's happening on Halopedia. Learn what tasks need to be done, what groups can be joined, and get or post news about recent events or current activities.</li>
<li>Questions? Check out our <b><a href="/Halopedia:FAQ" title="Halopedia:FAQ">FAQ</a></b>, or ask your own questions at the <b><a href="/Talk:Main_Page" title="Talk:Main Page">main page discussion</a></b> or at the <b><a href="/Halopedia_talk:Community" title="Halopedia talk:Community">community portal discussion</a></b>.</li>
<li>Want to help but don't know where to start? Head on over to the <b><a href="/Halopedia:Projects/Improvement" title="Halopedia:Projects/Improvement">Article Improvement Drive</a></b> page for a list of articles in need of improvement.</li>
<li>Get to know Halopedia's <b><a href="/Halopedia:Administrators" title="Halopedia:Administrators">administrators</a></b>!</li>
<li>Check out the <b><a href="/Special:WikiForum" title="Special:WikiForum">forums</a></b> to see what the community is working on, to give feedback or just to say <i>"hi"</i>, and chat with the Halopedia community on our <b><a href="/Halopedia:Discord_server" title="Halopedia:Discord server">Discord server</a></b>.</li></ul>
</div></div></div>
<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;">News</div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;">
<div class="center-template" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:0.5em; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold;"><a href="/News:Main" title="News:Main">Halopedia news</a></div>
<ul><li><b>November 4, 2019</b>: <a href="/News:Halo_News_Network_Issue_6_-_Believing_in_us_for_15_years" title="News:Halo News Network Issue 6 - Believing in us for 15 years">Halo News Network Issue 6 - Believing in us for 15 years</a></li>
<li><b>December 6, 2021</b>: <a href="/News:Halopedia_Reviews:_Divine_Wind" title="News:Halopedia Reviews: Divine Wind"><i>Halo: Divine Wind</i> - Halopedia Review</a></li>
<li><b>October 3, 2022</b>: <a href="/News:Halopedia_Reviews:_The_Rubicon_Protocol" title="News:Halopedia Reviews: The Rubicon Protocol"><i>Halo: The Rubicon Protocol</i> - Halopedia Review</a></li>
<li><b>September 8, 2023</b>: <a href="/News:Halopedia_Reviews:_Outcasts" title="News:Halopedia Reviews: Outcasts"><i>Halo: Outcasts</i> - Halopedia Review</a></li>
<li><b>May 1, 2024</b>: <a href="/News:Halopedia_Reviews:_Epitaph" title="News:Halopedia Reviews: Epitaph"><i>Halo: Epitaph</i> - Halopedia Review</a></li></ul>
<hr />
<div class="center-template" style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:0.5em; font-size:14px; font-weight:bold;">Official news</div>
<ul><li><i><a href="/Halo_Infinite" title="Halo Infinite">Halo Infinite</a></i>'s <b><a href="/Infinite_(Operation)" title="Infinite (Operation)">Operation: Infinite</a></b> released on November 18<sup>th</sup>! It features the addition of over 200 new customization items to <a href="/The_Exchange" class="mw-disambig" title="The Exchange">The Exchange</a>, a 100-tier Operation pass with several new <a href="/Armor_customization_(Halo_Infinite)" title="Armor customization (Halo Infinite)">armor customization</a> across various armor cores, permanent double XP boots to both <a href="/Rank_(Halo_Infinite)" title="Rank (Halo Infinite)">career rank</a> and <a href="/Spartan_Points" title="Spartan Points">Spartan Points</a>, and more. This is the final planned major content update for <i>Halo Infinite</i> as Halo Studios shifts focus to work on several new <i>Halo</i> titles.</li></ul>
<ul><li>During the <a href="/Halo_Championship_Series" title="Halo Championship Series">Halo Championship Series</a> in October 2025, <a href="/Halo_Studios" title="Halo Studios">Halo Studios</a> announced <i><a href="/Halo:_Campaign_Evolved" title="Halo: Campaign Evolved">Halo: Campaign Evolved</a></i>, a remake of the original <i><a href="/Halo:_Combat_Evolved" title="Halo: Combat Evolved">Halo: Combat Evolved</a></i> campaign, recreated in <a href="/Unreal_Engine" title="Unreal Engine">Unreal Engine 5</a>, following up on the <i><a href="/Project_Foundry" title="Project Foundry">Project Foundry</a></i> demo revealed in <a href="/2024" title="2024">2024</a>! A total remake rather than a graphical remaster, it includes remade gameplay, art, re-recorded voice acting and music, and new story content in the form of new prequel missions set before the story of the original game. Read more <span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.halowaypoint.com/news/introducing-halo-campaign-evolved"><b>HERE</b></a></span>!</li></ul>
<ul><li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Edge_of_Dawn" title="Halo: Edge of Dawn">Halo: Edge of Dawn</a></b></i>, a brand new <i>Halo</i> novel written by <a href="/Kelly_Gay" title="Kelly Gay">Kelly Gay</a>, releases on December 16<sup>th</sup>! It picks up in the immediate aftermath of <i>Halo Infinite</i>'s campaign, following <a href="/John-117" title="John-117">John-117</a>, <a href="/Fernando_Esparza" title="Fernando Esparza">Fernando Esparza</a>, and newly-named <a href="/Joyeuse" title="Joyeuse">Joyeuse</a> as the trio continues the fight for <a href="/Zeta_Halo" class="mw-redirect" title="Zeta Halo">Zeta Halo</a>, tying into the event of <i><a href="/Halo:_The_Rubicon_Protocol" title="Halo: The Rubicon Protocol">Halo: The Rubicon Protocol</a></i>. What's more is that the official audiobook for <i>Halo: Edge of Dawn</i> will be narrated by <a href="/Nicolas_Roye" title="Nicolas Roye">Nicolas Roye</a>, the voice actor for the Fernando Esparza, with <a href="/Steve_Downes" title="Steve Downes">Steve Downes</a>, <a href="/Jen_Taylor" title="Jen Taylor">Jen Taylor</a>, and <a href="/Debra_Wilson?action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="Debra Wilson (page does not exist)">Debra Wilson</a> also returning to lend their voices to their own respective characters!</li></ul>
<ul><li>The first volume of <i><b><a href="/Halo:_Waypoint_Chronicles" title="Halo: Waypoint Chronicles">Halo: Waypoint Chronicles</a></b></i>, a <i>Halo</i> short story anthology series, is set to release on May 26<sup>th</sup>! It compiles all 24 of the <a href="/Halo_Waypoint_Chronicle" title="Halo Waypoint Chronicle">Halo Waypoint Chronicles</a> previously only viewable online, along with <a href="/Halo_Infinite_Story_%26_Intel" title="Halo Infinite Story &amp; Intel"><i>Halo Infinite</i> Intel Drops</a>, <a href="/Armory_Infinitum" title="Armory Infinitum">Armory Infinitum</a> entries, <a href="/Story_Shard" title="Story Shard">Story Shards</a>, and ten entirely new stories into a single compendium!</li></ul>
<ul><li><b><a href="/Digsite" title="Digsite">Digsite</a></b>, a team composed of <a href="/343_Industries" class="mw-redirect" title="343 Industries">343 Industries</a> employees and community <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Video_game_modding" class="extiw" title="wikipedia:Video game modding">modders</a>, are busy restoring <a href="/Cut_content" class="mw-redirect" title="Cut content">cut content</a> from previous <i><a href="/Halo_(disambiguation)" class="mw-disambig" title="Halo (disambiguation)">Halo</a></i> games, such as <i><a href="/Halo:_Combat_Evolved" title="Halo: Combat Evolved">Halo: Combat Evolved</a></i> and <i><a href="/Halo_2" title="Halo 2">Halo 2</a></i>! An previous update to <i><a href="/Halo:_The_Master_Chief_Collection" title="Halo: The Master Chief Collection">Halo: The Master Chief Collection</a></i> on PC even allows modders to incorporate this restored content into their creations. Read more <span class="plainlinks"><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.halowaypoint.com/news/digsite-deliveries"><b>HERE</b></a></span>!</li></ul>
<hr />
<center><span class="plainlinks"><small><b><a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.halowaypoint.com/en-us/news">Halo Waypoint News</a>: <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.halowaypoint.com/en-us/news?categoryName=Canon%20Fodder">Canon Fodder</a> • <a target="_blank" rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://www.halowaypoint.com/en-us/news?categoryName=Halo%20Community%20Update">Community Update</a></b></small></span></center>
<hr />
