<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;"><a href="/Halopedia:Projects/Improvement" title="Halopedia:Projects/Improvement"><span style="color:#fff;">Article Improvement Drive</span></a></div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;text-align:left; color:#000; border-radius: 0 0 .5em .5em; padding: 0 0 4px 4px; background:#FAFAFA;">
<div class="floatright"><a href="/Halopedia:Projects/Improvement" title="Halopedia:Projects/Improvement"><img alt="Halopedia Improvement I WANT YOU.png" src="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e2/Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png/107px-Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="107" height="159" srcset="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e2/Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png/161px-Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png 1.5x, https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e2/Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png/214px-Halopedia_Improvement_I_WANT_YOU.png 2x" data-file-width="432" data-file-height="640" /></a></div>
<p><b><a href="/Halopedia:Projects/Improvement" title="Halopedia:Projects/Improvement">Article Improvement Drive</a></b> is a community project to improve the wiki's content through bringing articles in dire need of improvement—from cleanup to content expansion and updates—to everyone's attention. Anyone is welcome to participate in the project!
</p><p>A small sampling of articles in need of new content:
</p>
<ul><li><b><a href="/Veta_Lopis" title="Veta Lopis">Veta Lopis</a></b> (<i><a href="/Halo:_Retribution" title="Halo: Retribution">Halo: Retribution</a></i>)</li>
<li><b><a href="/Melody_Azikiwe" title="Melody Azikiwe">Melody Azikiwe</a></b> (<i><a href="/Halo:_Envoy" title="Halo: Envoy">Halo: Envoy</a></i>)</li>
<li><b><a href="/Gray_Team" title="Gray Team">Gray Team</a></b> (<i>Halo: Envoy</i>)</li>
<li><b><a href="/Rion_Forge" title="Rion Forge">Rion Forge</a></b> (<i><a href="/Halo:_Smoke_and_Shadow" title="Halo: Smoke and Shadow">Halo: Smoke and Shadow</a></i>, <i><a href="/Halo:_Renegades" title="Halo: Renegades">Halo: Renegades</a></i>)</li>
<li><b><a href="/Operation:_JOVIAN_WHISTLE" title="Operation: JOVIAN WHISTLE">Operation: JOVIAN WHISTLE</a></b> (<i><a href="/Halo:_Last_Light" title="Halo: Last Light">Halo: Last Light</a></i>)</li>
<li><b><a href="/Drifts_Randomly" title="Drifts Randomly">Drifts Randomly</a></b> (<i><a href="/Halo:_Hunters_in_the_Dark" title="Halo: Hunters in the Dark">Halo: Hunters in the Dark</a></i>)</li></ul>
<p>The following articles for <i>Halo</i> media could use the addition (or completion) of a <b>plot synopsis</b>:
</p>
<ul><li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Renegades" title="Halo: Renegades">Halo: Renegades</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Battle_Born" title="Halo: Battle Born">Halo: Battle Born</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Silent_Storm" title="Halo: Silent Storm">Halo: Silent Storm</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Bad_Blood" title="Halo: Bad Blood">Halo: Bad Blood</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Legacy_of_Onyx" title="Halo: Legacy of Onyx">Halo: Legacy of Onyx</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Retribution" title="Halo: Retribution">Halo: Retribution</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Envoy" title="Halo: Envoy">Halo: Envoy</a></b></i></li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Halo:_Smoke_and_Shadow" title="Halo: Smoke and Shadow">Halo: Smoke and Shadow</a></b></i> (Part Four)</li>
<li><i><b><a href="/Promises_to_Keep" title="Promises to Keep">Promises to Keep</a></b></i></li></ul>
<hr />
See the <a href="/Halopedia:Projects/Improvement" title="Halopedia:Projects/Improvement">AID project page</a> for more information!</div>
</div>
<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;">Did you know?</div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;">
<ul><li>...that <b><a href="/Oly_Oly_Oxen_Free" class="mw-redirect" title="Oly Oly Oxen Free">Oly Oly Oxen Free</a></b> is a six-note tone used by <a href="/SPARTAN-II_program" title="SPARTAN-II program">SPARTAN-IIs</a> as an all-clear signal?</li>
<li>...that <b><a href="/Corbulo_Academy_of_Military_Science" title="Corbulo Academy of Military Science">Corbulo Academy of Military Science</a></b> was a UNSC <a href="/Officer_Candidate_School" title="Officer Candidate School">military academy</a> mainly attended by the offspring of high-ranked officials?</li>
<li>...that <b><a href="/Seaward" title="Seaward">Seaward</a></b> was a low-tech <a href="/Forerunner" title="Forerunner">Forerunner</a> retreat world and the <a href="/Flood" title="Flood">Flood</a>'s first target in the <a href="/Forerunner-Flood_war" title="Forerunner-Flood war">Forerunner-Flood war</a>?</li>
<li>...that <i><a href="/Mantle%27s_Approach" title="Mantle&#39;s Approach">Mantle's Approach</a></i>, the <a href="/Ur-Didact" title="Ur-Didact">Didact</a>'s flagship in <i><a href="/Halo_4" title="Halo 4">Halo 4</a></i>, is over 371 kilometers tall?</li>
<li>...that <i><a href="/Halo_2" title="Halo 2">Halo 2</a></i> modding shows that <a href="/Cortana" title="Cortana">Cortana</a> has animations for some weapons, such as the <a href="/Type-25_plasma_rifle" class="mw-redirect" title="Type-25 plasma rifle">Plasma Rifle</a>?</li></ul>
<hr />
<small>• <a href="/Halopedia:Featured/DYK" title="Halopedia:Featured/DYK">Add your own <i>Did you know?</i></a></small></div>
</div>
</td>
<td style="width:260px" valign="top">
<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;"><a href="/Halopedia:Featured/Article" title="Halopedia:Featured/Article"><span style="color:#fff">Featured article</span></a>:<br /><a href="/Sali_%27Nyon" title="Sali &#39;Nyon"><span style="color:#fff">Sali 'Nyon</span></a></div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;text-align:justify; color:#000; border-radius:0 0 .5em .5em; padding:0; background:#FAFAFA;">
<div class="center"><div class="floatnone"><a href="/Sali_%27Nyon" title="Sali &#39;Nyon"><img alt="Sali &#39;Nyon" src="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/d/d3/Enc22_Nyon.jpg/270px-Enc22_Nyon.jpg" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="270" height="371" srcset="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/d/d3/Enc22_Nyon.jpg/405px-Enc22_Nyon.jpg 1.5x, https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/d/d3/Enc22_Nyon.jpg/540px-Enc22_Nyon.jpg 2x" data-file-width="950" data-file-height="1306" /></a></div></div><div style="padding: 4px 8px 0">
<p>Native to the Sangheili colony of Eudolaan, Sali 'Nyon was an exceptional warrior within the Covenant military, earning the rank of zealot commander and a personal commendation from the High Prophet of Mercy. After the war, Sali 'Nyon joined Jul 'Mdama in his attempted resurrection of the Covenant, though ultimately began to question the Supreme Commander's true motivations. Fashioning himself as the true Hand of the Didact, he began to amass his own followers from within 'Mdama's forces, and attempted a coup during the Battle of Aktis IV. Despite failing and becoming imprisoned by 'Mdama, Sali 'Nyon would once again enact an insurrection with the help of ONI operative Ayit 'Sevi, this time successfully rallying followers to his cause and escaping with the <i>Kerel</i>-pattern assault carrier <i>Breath of Annihilation</i>. Eventually, Sali 'Nyon allied with High Lord Dovo Nesto, the fanatical San'Shyuum leader of the Order of Restoration. However, during an attempt to access the Domain on the human colony of Boundary, Sali 'Nyon was killed by War Chief Severan of the Banished while defending Dovo Nesto.
</p>
</div><div style="text-align:right"><i><a href="/Sali_%27Nyon" title="Sali &#39;Nyon">Read more...</a></i></div>
<hr />
<center><b>Nominate a featured article <a href="/Halopedia_talk:Featured/Article/Nomination" title="Halopedia talk:Featured/Article/Nomination">here</a>!</b></center></div>
</div>
<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="How_to_change_the_article">How to change the article</span></h2>
<p>To change the featured article, you need to update the following code:
<code>{{Halopedia:Main Page/Featured/Layout|Name|File:|Description}}</code>
</p>
<ul><li>Name = The name of the article.</li>
<li>File: = The file name goes here, this needs the "File:" part.</li>
<li>Description = The article description goes here.&lt;/noinclude&gt;</li></ul>
<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;">Featured quote</div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;">
<div style="padding-top:6px">
<table class="quotebox" style="margin:auto;">
<tbody><tr>
<td valign="top" style="width:20px; font-size:36px; font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:left; padding:3px;">“
</td>
<td valign="top" style="padding:3px;">
<p><i>Doctor Halsey and her Spartans deserve the <b>utmost</b> respect, Colonel. And if you wish to keep your newly acquired position on the Security Council, you will show them that respect, or I will personally kick you from here to Melbourne. Those "freaks" have more confirmed kills than any three divisions of ODSTs and have garnered every major citation the UNSC awards. Those "freaks" have personally saved my life twice, as well the lives of most of the senior staff here at HighCom. Keep your bigotry in check, Colonel. Do you understand?!!</i><br />
<span style="float:right;">&#8212;<a href="/Terrence_Hood" title="Terrence Hood">Lord Terrence Hood</a>, <i><a href="/Halo:_First_Strike" title="Halo: First Strike">Halo: First Strike</a></i></span>
</p>
</td>
<td valign="bottom" style="width:20px; font-size:36px; font-family:&#39;Times New Roman&#39;, serif; font-weight:bold; text-align:right; padding:3px;">”
</td></tr></tbody></table>
</div>
<hr />
<div style="text-align:center; font-size:smaller;"><a href="/Halopedia_talk:Featured/Quote" title="Halopedia talk:Featured/Quote">Nominate and vote for your favorite quote!</a></div></div>
</div>
<div class="containerTem" style="background:#666;border-radius:0.5em;padding:0 2px 2px;margin:0 auto 16px;"><div class="containerTitle" style="color:#fff;text-align:center;font-size:115%;font-weight:bold;"><div class="floatleft"><img alt="Discord-icon.png" src="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e9/Discord-icon.png/20px-Discord-icon.png" decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="20" height="20" srcset="https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e9/Discord-icon.png/30px-Discord-icon.png 1.5x, https://halo.wiki.gallery/images/thumb/e/e9/Discord-icon.png/40px-Discord-icon.png 2x" data-file-width="1600" data-file-height="1600" /></div> <a href="/Halopedia:Discord_server" title="Halopedia:Discord server"><span style="color:#fff">Community chat</span></a></div><div class="containerContent" style="clear:both;overflow:auto;background:#FAFAFA;border-radius:0 0 0.5em 0.5em;padding:2px 4px 1px;overflow:visible; text-align:center; color:#000; font-size:110%; border-radius:0 0 .5em .5em; padding:0 4px; background:#23272a;">
